  "text": [
    "1",
    "These guys try to make us",
    "match moods to products",
    "the way once,",
    "under love\u2019s spell,",
    "we attached meaning",
    "to sound,",
    "attached sounds to objects.",
    "The old magic won\u2019t work now,",
    "but it\u2019s nice",
    "to be reminded of it.",
    "2",
    "She\u2019s a tease,",
    "tears her skirts off",
    "one by one.",
    "Really?",
    "Drops her petals",
    "as if she could always",
    "make more.",
    "It\u2019s tiresome.",
    "We know",
    "what she looks like",
    "naked.",
    "On a cold night,",
    "we can see forever."
  ],
  "title": "The Thinning",
  "year": ""
}